sub_title: Manager of Customer Success & Customer Care Belgium & The Netherlands at GoStudent
summary: I am a data-driven manager with experience in successfully launching, growing, and professionalizing departments (Sales, Customer Success, Customer Care) within start-ups/scale-ups. I easily translate strategic topics into tangible operational objectives and communicate them clearly to the workforce. In essence, I love making complicated things simple. I bring a commercial mindset, data savviness, and I am not afraid to make my hands dirty. I thrive in an innovative work environment with ample opportunities for initiative, freedom to pioneer, and a culture of action.
